    "fullRecordText": "Artwork Record / 作品档案\nArtwork ID: KXW-O-063\nTitle (CN): 红裙\nTitle (EN): The Red Dress\nYear: 2006\nMedium: Oil on Canvas\nDimensions: 75 × 90 cm\nSeries (CN): 光与生命\nSeries (EN): Light and Life\nArtwork Statement (CN)\n《红裙》创作于2006年，是艺术家早期人物油画作品。画中女子静坐长椅，闭目沉思，红色长裙与蓝色背景形成鲜明对比，营造出宁静而内敛的精神氛围。人物并未与观者对视，而是沉浸于内在世界，作品借由简洁的构图与克制的色彩表达女性内心的平静、独立与生命的沉静力量。\nArtwork Statement (EN)\nThe Red Dress, painted in 2006, is an early figurative oil painting by the artist. A woman sits quietly on a bench with her eyes closed, immersed in contemplation. The contrast between the vivid red dress and the cool blue background creates a calm and introspective atmosphere. Through a restrained composition, the painting reflects inner peace, quiet strength, and the enduring vitality of the human spirit.\nKeywords / 关键词\n中文：女性、红裙、肖像、宁静、内省、生命English: Woman, Red Dress, Portrait, Serenity, Contemplation, Life\nExhibition History / 展览经历\n待更新 / To be updated\nAwards / 荣誉\n待更新 / To be updated\nCollection / 收藏\n待更新 / To be updated\nPublication / 出版发表\n待更新 / To be updated",
