    "statementZh": "《苗族少女》创作于2001年，以苗族少女的肖像为主题。画中人物面带真挚笑容，身着民族服饰，佩戴传统银饰，温暖的光线映照出人物纯真而自信的神情。作品不仅记录了少数民族独特的文化风貌，也赞美了人与土地共同孕育出的生命力与人文精神，是艺术家早期人物创作的重要代表之一。",
    "statementEn": "Painted in 2001, Miao Girl portrays a young woman of the Miao ethnic community wearing traditional attire and silver ornaments. Her genuine smile and the warm light create a vivid sense of vitality and cultural identity. Beyond portraiture, the work celebrates the dignity of rural life, ethnic traditions, and the enduring beauty of human character.",
