    "fullRecordText": "Artwork Record / 作品档案\nArtwork ID: KXW-W-066\nTitle (CN): 采茶去\nTitle (EN): Heading to the Tea Fields\nYear: 2020\nMedium: Watercolor on Paper\nDimensions: 30 × 55 cm\nSeries (CN): 田园诗\nSeries (EN): Pastoral Poems\nArtwork Statement (CN)\n《采茶去》取材于乡村劳动场景，描绘一位采茶妇女肩背竹篓、步履坚定地前往茶园。作品保留了大面积留白，使人物成为画面的精神中心。艺术家关注普通劳动者平凡而真实的生命状态，通过细腻的水彩语言刻画岁月在面容上的痕迹，表现人与土地、劳动与生活之间朴素而深厚的联系。\nArtwork Statement (EN)\nHeading to the Tea Fields portrays a rural tea picker on her way to work. Against a spacious white background, the figure becomes the emotional focus of the composition. Rather than documenting labor alone, the watercolor honors dignity, resilience, and the enduring relationship between people, work, and the land.\nKeywords / 关键词\n中文：乡村、采茶、劳动者、人物、水彩、土地English: Rural Life, Tea Picking, Worker, Figure, Watercolor, Land\nExhibition History / 展览经历\n待更新 / To be updated\nAwards / 荣誉\n待更新 / To be updated\nCollection / 收藏\n待更新 / To be updated\nPublication / 出版发表\n待更新 / To be updated",
