    "dimensions": "50 cm（Diameter）",
    "series": "Light and Life（光与生命）",
    "category": "oil",
    "image": "assets/images/artworks-web/catalogue-raisonne/KXW-051-2000.jpg",
    "keywords": "English:Flowers · Still Life · Spring · Ceramic Vase · Color · Oil Painting · Light · Harmony\n中文：花卉 · 静物 · 春天 · 陶瓷花瓶 · 色彩 · 油画 · 光 · 和谐",
    "statementZh": "《春日花语》创作于2026年，以圆形画幅描绘盛开的花束与果实静物。作品以明亮的黄色背景衬托花卉的生命力，将器物、花朵与果实组织成充满节奏与色彩关系的画面。圆形构图强化了凝聚感，也赋予作品温暖、完整的视觉体验。作品关注日常生活中的美感与生命气息，通过富有表现力的色彩和自由的笔触，展现自然丰盛、生机盎然的状态，传递平凡生活中的喜悦与希望。",
    "statementEn": "Spring Blossoms was completed in 2026. Painted on a circular canvas, the work presents a vibrant bouquet and seasonal fruit in a decorative ceramic vase. A luminous yellow background enhances the vitality of the flowers, while expressive brushwork and rich color relationships create a joyful and harmonious composition.The painting celebrates the beauty of everyday life, transforming an ordinary still life into a visual expression of abundance, warmth, and the enduring vitality of nature.",
