    "artworkId": "KXW-O-053",
    "titleZh": "《花语》",
    "titleEn": "Language of Flowers",
    "year": "2024",
    "medium": "Oil on Canvas（布面油画）",
    "dimensions": "30 × 40 cm",
    "series": "Still Life（静物）",
    "category": "oil",
    "image": "assets/images/artworks-web/catalogue-raisonne/KXW-053-2000.jpg",
    "keywords": "English:Flowers · Still Life · Basket · Roses · Oil Painting · Color · Quietness · Daily Life\n中文：花卉 · 静物 · 花篮 · 玫瑰 · 油画 · 色彩 · 宁静 · 日常",
    "statementZh": "《花语》创作于2024年。作品以一篮鲜花为主体，在浅绿色背景的映衬下营造出温柔而安静的空间氛围。粉色玫瑰与暖色花朵相互交织，黑色花篮形成稳定的视觉重心，使画面在轻盈与沉静之间取得平衡。作品关注日常生活中的诗意瞬间，通过简洁的构图和富有层次的油画笔触，表现花朵短暂而灿烂的生命状态，传达平凡生活中蕴藏的温暖、希望与美感。",
    "statementEn": "Language of Flowers was completed in 2024. The painting features a basket of fresh flowers against a soft green background, creating a calm and intimate atmosphere. Pink roses and warm blossoms contrast with the dark basket, establishing a harmonious balance between lightness and stability.Rather than depicting flowers as decoration, the work reflects the quiet poetry of everyday life. Through expressive brushwork and restrained composition, it celebrates beauty, tenderness, and the fleeting vitality of nature.",
