    "keywords": "English:Pelicans · Wetland · Ecology · Habitat · Oil Painting · Nature · Water Reflection · Coexistence\n中文：鹈鹕 · 湿地 · 生态 · 栖息地 · 油画 · 自然 · 水面倒影 · 共生",
    "statementZh": "《栖息之境》创作于2024年。作品描绘湿地岛屿上成群栖息的鹈鹕，在繁茂植被与碧绿水面的映衬下形成宁静而富有生命力的自然景观。画面通过丰富的绿色层次、水面倒影与鸟群姿态，呈现生态环境的稳定与和谐。作品关注人与自然共同生存的生态命题，并非强调戏剧性叙事，而是以平静的日常场景表达生命共同体的价值。油画厚实的笔触强化了植被、水体与羽毛的质感，使自然成为持续孕育生命的空间。",
    "statementEn": "Sanctuary was completed in 2024. The painting portrays a group of pelicans resting on a small wetland island surrounded by lush vegetation and emerald water. Reflections, layered greens, and the quiet presence of the birds create a peaceful ecological landscape.Rather than presenting dramatic narratives, the work celebrates coexistence between wildlife and nature. Through expressive oil brushwork, it transforms an ordinary habitat into a meditation on ecological balance and the continuity of life.",
    "exhibitionHistory": "中文：\n• 暂无。\n\nEnglish:\n• None at present.",
    "awards": "",
    "collection": "",
    "publication": "中文：\n• 暂无。\n\nEnglish:\n• None at present.",
    "fullRecordText": "Artwork Record / 作品档案\nArtwork ID: KXW-O-055\nTitle (CN): 《栖息之境》\nTitle (EN): Sanctuary\nYear: 2024\nMedium: Oil on Canvas（布面油画）\nDimensions: 80 × 100 cm\nSeries (CN): Nature and Ecology（自然与生态）\nSeries (EN): \nArtwork Statement (CN)\n《栖息之境》创作于2024年。作品描绘湿地岛屿上成群栖息的鹈鹕，在繁茂植被与碧绿水面的映衬下形成宁静而富有生命力的自然景观。画面通过丰富的绿色层次、水面倒影与鸟群姿态，呈现生态环境的稳定与和谐。作品关注人与自然共同生存的生态命题，并非强调戏剧性叙事，而是以平静的日常场景表达生命共同体的价值。油画厚实的笔触强化了植被、水体与羽毛的质感，使自然成为持续孕育生命的空间。\nArtwork Statement (EN)\nSanctuary was completed in 2024. The painting portrays a group of pelicans resting on a small wetland island surrounded by lush vegetation and emerald water. Reflections, layered greens, and the quiet presence of the birds create a peaceful ecological landscape.Rather than presenting dramatic narratives, the work celebrates coexistence between wildlife and nature. Through expressive oil brushwork, it transforms an ordinary habitat into a meditation on ecological balance and the continuity of life.\nKeywords / 关键词\nEnglish:Pelicans · Wetland · Ecology · Habitat · Oil Painting · Nature · Water Reflection · Coexistence\n中文：鹈鹕 · 湿地 · 生态 · 栖息地 · 油画 · 自然 · 水面倒影 · 共生\nExhibition History / 展览经历\n中文：\n• 暂无。\n\nEnglish:\n• None at present.\nPublication / 出版发表\n中文：\n• 暂无。\n\nEnglish:\n• None at present.",
