    "artworkId": "KXW-W-014",
    "titleZh": "《酱色右玉》",
    "titleEn": "Earth Tones of Youyu",
    "year": "2024",
    "medium": "Watercolor on Paper（纸本水彩）",
    "dimensions": "39 × 54 cm",
    "series": "Pastoral Poems（田园诗）",
    "category": "watercolor",
    "image": "assets/images/artworks-web/catalogue-raisonne/KXW-014-2000.jpg",
    "keywords": "English:Youyu · Earth · Soil · Rural Road · Tricycle · Landscape · Time · Watercolor中文：右玉 · 土地 · 酱色 · 乡村道路 · 三轮车 · 风土 · 时间 · 水彩",
    "statementZh": "《酱色右玉》取景于山西右玉。作品以当地厚重的酱色土地为视觉核心，乡间道路、三轮车与起伏的坡地共同构成朴素而真实的乡土景观。画面没有刻意营造戏剧性，而是通过土地本身的色彩、质感与光线变化，呈现人与自然长期共处所沉淀出的生活气息。水彩透明与叠加的语言，使土地既保有厚重感，又具有呼吸般的生命力。",
    "statementEn": "Inspired by the landscape of Youyu, Shanxi, Earth Tones of Youyu centers on the rich brown earth that defines the region. A rural road, a three-wheeled vehicle, and gently rolling fields create an understated yet authentic landscape. Through layered transparent watercolor, the painting reveals the enduring relationship between people, land, and time.",
    "exhibitionHistory": "中文：\n• 2024 入选“2024潮汕水彩年展——全国小幅水彩作品展”。\n• 展览于2024年12月在南澳县文化馆举行。\n\nEnglish:",
