    "fullRecordText": "Artwork Record / 作品档案\nArtwork ID: KXW-W-014\nTitle (CN): 《酱色右玉》\nTitle (EN): Earth Tones of Youyu\nYear: 2024\nMedium: Watercolor on Paper（纸本水彩）\nDimensions: 39 × 54 cm\nSeries (CN): Pastoral Poems（田园诗）\nSeries (EN): \nArtwork Statement (CN)\n《酱色右玉》取景于山西右玉。作品以当地厚重的酱色土地为视觉核心，乡间道路、三轮车与起伏的坡地共同构成朴素而真实的乡土景观。画面没有刻意营造戏剧性，而是通过土地本身的色彩、质感与光线变化，呈现人与自然长期共处所沉淀出的生活气息。水彩透明与叠加的语言，使土地既保有厚重感，又具有呼吸般的生命力。\nArtwork Statement (EN)\nInspired by the landscape of Youyu, Shanxi, Earth Tones of Youyu centers on the rich brown earth that defines the region. A rural road, a three-wheeled vehicle, and gently rolling fields create an understated yet authentic landscape. Through layered transparent watercolor, the painting reveals the enduring relationship between people, land, and time.\nKeywords / 关键词\nEnglish:Youyu · Earth · Soil · Rural Road · Tricycle · Landscape · Time · Watercolor中文：右玉 · 土地 · 酱色 · 乡村道路 · 三轮车 · 风土 · 时间 · 水彩\nExhibition History / 展览经历\n中文：\n• 2024 入选“2024潮汕水彩年展——全国小幅水彩作品展”。\n• 展览于2024年12月在南澳县文化馆举行。\n\nEnglish:\nPublication / 出版发表\n中文：\n• 暂无。\n\nEnglish:\n• None to date.",
