    "image": "assets/images/artworks-web/catalogue-raisonne/KXW-040-2000.jpg",
    "keywords": "English:Dong Village · Firewood · Daily Life · Smoke · Rural Landscape · Memory · Pastel · Humanity中文：侗寨 · 炊烟 · 日常生活 · 柴火 · 乡村风景 · 记忆 · 色粉 · 人文",
    "statementZh": "《侗家炊烟》完成于2022年。作品取材于贵州侗寨采风。画面没有直接描绘人物，而是以层层堆积的木柴、覆盖其上的蓝绿色防雨布，以及隐约可见的村寨空间，呈现山地聚落最真实的生活景象。木柴既是冬日取暖与日常炊事的物质基础，也是乡村生活延续至今的重要记忆。我关注的是那些容易被忽略的生活细节。炊烟并未直接出现，却通过木柴与空间暗示着它的存在。作品希望借由色粉丰富而沉稳的层次，将普通乡村中的劳动、生活与时间沉淀，转化为具有诗意与温度的视觉经验。",
    "statementEn": "Smoke over the Dong Village was completed in 2022 after field research in a Dong village in Guizhou, China. Rather than depicting people directly, the work focuses on piles of firewood, blue-green protective tarps, and the quiet village environment. Firewood serves as both a practical necessity for cooking and heating and as a lasting symbol of rural memory.The work pays attention to overlooked details of everyday life. Although smoke is never literally shown, its presence is suggested through the materials and the surrounding space. Through the rich textures and subtle tonal variations of pastel, the painting transforms ordinary rural scenes into a poetic reflection on labor, memory, and the enduring rhythm of village life.",
