    "fullRecordText": "Artwork Record / 作品档案\nArtwork ID: KXW-HP-041\nTitle (CN): 《红樱桃》\nTitle (EN): Red Cherries\nYear: 2024\nMedium: Pastel on Paper（纸本色粉）\nDimensions: 22 ×28 cm\nSeries (CN): Light and Life（光与生命）\nSeries (EN): \nArtwork Statement (CN)\n《红樱桃》完成于2024年。作品以成熟樱桃为对象，通过密集的构图与饱满的色彩，呈现果实在光照下丰富的层次变化。每一颗樱桃既保持独立的形态，又共同构成充满节奏感的整体画面。我希望通过最普通的水果，表达生命旺盛而真实的状态。色粉细腻的颗粒感强化了果实的质感，也让光线在色彩之间流动，使日常事物散发出自然、温暖而充满生命力的光彩。\nArtwork Statement (EN)\nRed Cherries was completed in 2024. Focusing on ripe cherries, the work explores the richness of light, color, and texture through a dense composition. Each fruit maintains its individuality while contributing to a rhythmic visual whole.Using an ordinary subject, the painting celebrates the vitality of everyday life. The delicate texture of pastel enhances the luminous surface of the cherries, allowing light to move naturally across the composition and revealing the quiet abundance found in simple things.\nKeywords / 关键词\nEnglish:Cherry · Fruit · Light · Vitality · Color · Still Life · Pastel · Nature中文：樱桃 · 果实 · 光线 · 生命力 · 色彩 · 静物 · 色粉 · 自然\nExhibition History / 展览经历\n中文：\n• 暂无公开展览记录。\n\nEnglish:\nPublication / 出版发表\n中文：\n• 收录个人作品档案。\n\nEnglish:\n• Included in the artist's portfolio.",
